---
title: Asparagus Pizza Bianca with Fresh Mozzarella and Basil
description: It's flatbread night with a veggie twist. Pan-seared asparagus,  herbaceous basil, thinly sliced shallots, fresh mozzarella and a sweet finish of fig jam. It's flatbread redefined!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/asparagus-pizza-bianca-9006818e.jpg
